main event: On 28 Jan 61, at 1830, a witness observed a dark gray object moving from East to West, resembling the size of a jet plane without wings.
interesting points: The observation lasted for 1 minute.,The object disappeared behind a house.,The witness stated it looked like a jet plane., The sighting was similar to one reported on 7 Jan 61., The object was estimated to travel at about 325 miles per hour.
sighted object: dark gray object, about the size of a jet plane
witness description: male, 35 years old, active member of the U.F.O. Club
